    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Summer/été 1999\nFlight Schedule\nHoraire des Vols\neffective 01Apr99-310ct99\nen vigueur 01avr99-31oct99\nCANADA\n3000\nFirst Edition\nPremière édition\nTICKETS:\nIssued March 15, 199\n1-877-359-2263\nCANADA 3000",
      "[Remind you of anything?]\nBlackout periods. The times when other travel point\nprograms won't let you fly on the points you've earned.\nWhat's worse, they occur when most people want\nto fly. But with these cards, there is no blackout or\nlimited seat allocations. So, anytime Canada 3000\nseats are available, they're yours. Isn't that the way it\nshould be? To apply, call 1-800-611-8472.\nCitizens Bank T\n2798 2000 0000 3000\nVISA®\nVISA\nTo fly free fast,\nyou'll need the right card.\nEarn one travel point for every dollar spent.\n*VanCity, Licensee of Mark. Travel points are earned on purchases, less\nreturns, but not on cash advances, convenience cheques, fees, interest\ncharges or applicable taxes."
    ],
